(Codebase Architect Explainer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1\) Big Picture) Tj
T*
(This project is a Node.js Express backend API focused on authentication and user management.) Tj
T*
(It provides health endpoints, request validation, user signup persistence in PostgreSQL,) Tj
T*
(and JWT cookie issuance.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\) Core Architecture) Tj
T*
(The codebase follows a layered monolith architecture:) Tj
T*
(- Entry/bootstrap: src/index.js -> src/server.js -> src/app.js) Tj
T*
(- HTTP transport: src/routes) Tj
T*
(- Controller layer: src/controllers) Tj
T*
(- Service/business layer: src/services) Tj
T*
(- Persistence/schema: src/models + src/config/database.js + drizzle migrations) Tj
T*
(- Shared utilities and validation: src/utils + src/validations + src/config/logger.js) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(High-level flow:) Tj
T*
(Client Request) Tj
T*
(  -> Express middleware stack in app.js) Tj
T*
(  -> /api/auth routes) Tj
T*
(  -> controller validation and orchestration) Tj
T*
(  -> service DB operations via Drizzle) Tj
T*
(  -> response + cookie + logs) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\) Key Components) Tj
T*
(- src/app.js: middleware, logging, health routes, API route mounting) Tj
T*
(- src/routes/auth.routes.js: route definitions) Tj
T*
(- src/controllers/auth.controller.js: signup request handling) Tj
T*
(- src/services/auth.service.js: user lookup/create and password hashing) Tj
T*
(- src/models/user.model.js: users table schema) Tj
T*
(- src/validations/auth.validation.js: Zod input schemas) Tj
T*
(- src/utils/jwt.js and src/utils/cookies.js: token and cookie helpers) Tj
T*
(- src/config/logger.js: Winston logging setup) Tj
T*
(- src/config/database.js: Neon + Drizzle database connection) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\) Data Flow and Communication) Tj
T*
(1. Request enters Express middleware.) Tj
T*
(2. Route dispatches to auth controller.) Tj
T*
(3. Controller validates payload with Zod.) Tj
T*
(4. Controller calls service.) Tj
T*
(5. Service queries/inserts using Drizzle against Postgres \(Neon\).) Tj
T*
(6. Controller signs JWT, sets HTTP-only cookie, and returns JSON.) Tj
T*
(7. Morgan and Winston capture logs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5\) Tech Stack and Dependencies) Tj
T*
(- express: HTTP server and routing) Tj
T*
(- drizzle-orm + drizzle-kit: data access and migrations) Tj
T*
(- @neondatabase/serverless: PostgreSQL connectivity) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
